# Scoped to tenantforge/Dockerfile (BuildKit honours <dockerfile>.dockerignore). Patterns are
# relative to the build context (the repo root). Keep the context lean + never ship build cruft.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.git
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/coverage
**/reports
**/.stryker-tmp
**/.turbo
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/docs/api
